SUMMARY:Writing Workshop: From Anecdote to Story
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website\n\nFor writers of fiction and memoir: Are you good 
 at writing sketches\, but not sure if they add up to a scene or a story? 
 Would you like to boost the emotion quotient (EQ) and play down mere 
 reportage of events in your work? Through exercises\, we’ll practice ways 
 to “thicken up” our writing and share supportive feedback. No 
 homework\; write in class. \n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Writing
