SUMMARY:English for Speakers of Other Languages (ESOL) for Beginners
DESCRIPTION:English for Speakers of Other Languages (ESOL) for Beginners is 
 designed to assist adult students in mastering the English language by 
 emphasizing speaking\, listening\, reading\, and writing skills. 
 \n\nStudents should bring their own notebook and pencils for note 
 taking.\n\nRegistration is required. Please notify us at 
 adultprograms@montclairlibrary.org if you are going to miss class. If you 
 do not attend the classes without notifying us\, you will not be allowed to 
