SUMMARY:(CANCELLED DUE TO WEATHER) Mah Jongg: Open Play
DESCRIPTION:Open Play is the perfect setting for players who know the 
 basics and want to enjoy friendly games\, practice their skills\, and build 
 confidence at the table. We'll bring the tiles\, and all the accessories.  
 You bring your 2025 National Mah Jongg League card and your love of the 
 game! The focus is on learning to play independently\, building 
 camaraderie\, and having fun. Come meet fellow Mah Jongg enthusiasts\, 
 sharpen your strategies\, and enjoy the lively spirit of the 
 game!\n\nStudents must know the basics of mah jongg.  If you're new to the 
 game\, or don't feel comfortable sitting at a table and playing with others 
 at a similar level\, please register for a Beginner class by clicking here. 
 Skip dates are Feb. 9th and 16th.\n\n \n\nPLEASE NOTE:\n\n\n	Students 
 should have taken Beginner Mah Jongg or have equivalent knowledge and 
 experience. \n\n\nStudents should bring the 2025 National Mah Jongg League 
 card to Open Play.
