SUMMARY:Beginner Mah Jongg - Thursday Evenings in February - BAB
DESCRIPTION:Looking for more fun in your life? Need an excuse to see your 
 friends without eating? Worried about dementia? Learn how to play the 
 ancient Chinese game of Mah Jongg! This game is not hard to play but 
 complex to learn. Our instructor's method of teaching is guaranteed to have 
 you playing with strategy by the end of the session.  This class will 
 prepare you for both online and in-person games.\n\nNOTE: If you know you 
 cannot attend any of the first 3 sessions\, please do not register for this 
 class.
