SUMMARY:Teen Book Club (Ages 12 - 18)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Teen Book Club -- each meeting\, we read books from 
 a different theme or genre and discuss! We meet on the second Thursday of 
 every other month.\nRegistration is required.\n\nJoin us in the Tower Room 
 on the Second Floor of the Library. If you need assistance finding us\, ask 
 the Reference Desk staff!\n\nSeptember 11\, 2025: Latinx Authors & Voices 
 in honor of Hispanic Heritage Month\n\nOctober 16\, 2025: Short 
 Stories\n\nNovember 13\, 2025: Native American & Indigenous Voices in honor 
 of Native American Heritage Month\n\nJanuary 8\, 2026: New 
 Beginnings\n\nMarch 12\, 2026: Sports\n\nMay 28\, 2026: THEME TBD -- We 
 will be in the First Floor Teen Room for our May meeting.\n\nSign up for 
 the Monthly Teen Newsletter\n
