SUMMARY:Manga Workshop for Parents (Ages 6-12)
DESCRIPTION:Do You have a huge Pokémon fan? Is your child starting to ask 
 about manga and anime? Maybe you’re just curious about the hype around 
 manga and anime.\n\nWell this workshop is for you!\n\nJoin us as we explore 
 the different genres within anime/manga\, how manga is beneficial to 
 readers\, and how to navigate the growing landscape that is 
 manga!\n\nParents will get to take home sheets listing several manga terms 
 and a book list of some of the manga we have in our collection.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Storytime Room\, Montclair Public Library
