SUMMARY:Silent Book Club Montclair
DESCRIPTION:At Silent Book Club® there's no assigned reading. SBC members 
 gather in bars\, cafés\, bookstores\, libraries\, and online to read 
 together in quiet camaraderie. All readers are welcome—ebooks or 
 audiobooks\, poetry or prose\, fiction or non-fiction... it's 
 BYOBook.\n\n\nDid you love silent reading time in school? Are you more of 
 an introvert that loves books\, but doesn't want to jump into a discussion 
 group? Are you looking to read more\, but struggle to sit down and just DO 
 IT? If you answered 'yes' to any of these\, you might like Silent Book 
 Club! Each month\, we meet around Montclair and enjoy each other's company 
 with a book of our own choosing.\n\nRegistration is required. Location 
 TBD.\n\nPlease be advised this book club will be meeting at a public 
 location and therefore cannot guarantee a quiet reading environment. This 
 book club is best for readers who enjoy a coffeeshop ambiance (low 
 chatter\, music\, outside noise\, etc.) or those who prefer to read with 
 headphones.
LOCATION:Montclair - Offsite
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Book Club
