SUMMARY:The Penny Power Project: Financial Literacy for Kids (Grades 2-5)
DESCRIPTION:The Penny Power Project aims to teach the students about the 
 essentials of financial literacy. Throughout the three-week course\, the 
 program will cover various topics like budgeting\, saving\, investing\, 
 loans\, the history of money\, the functions of money\, exchange rates\, 
 and how interest works. Additionally\, the course will also instruct 
 students on how they can apply what they’ve learned to their lives 
 through fun activities and videos.\n\n
