SUMMARY:Black Women in Biopic: Hidden Figures (2016)
DESCRIPTION:Hidden Figures (2016) | PG\, 127mins\n\nThree female 
 African-American mathematicians provide crucial calculations for NASA's 
 space race against the Soviets\, all while dealing with the racist and 
 sexist assumptions of their white co-workers. Watch the trailer 
